snippet.title: SauceyDad
snippet.description:
Welcome to SauceyDad’s Reactions!

Thank you for stopping by the channel, I hope you enjoy the content! If you do, go on ahead and punch that Subscribe button square in the eye! Then come rite back with a jab to that little bell, so you never miss an upload!

On this channel we react to anything that might be of interest to either SauceyDad, or his fam...which is YOU!

We’ll mainly be focusing on the highly controversial world that is the paranormal. Having grown up in a very haunted house I have spent my life trying to learn more about spirits and what happens to our “energy” after our time on this earth has come to an end. 

All I want from you, is video recommendations! I ask that anytime you come across something that makes your hair stand on end, and your blood run cold, that you drop it in the comments so we can “get scared” together!

To keep up with SauceyDad, follow the socials! 

TikTok & Twitter: @SauceyDad
Instagram: @Sauceydadd

Thank you all and welcome to #TeamSaucey!!
